        "content": "## ‚öñÔ∏è AI Contract Reviewer\n\n**Your First-Pass Legal Assistant.**\nPaste a contract draft, and **Gemini** (acting as a lawyer) will review it for risks, missing clauses, and unfair terms.\n\n**How it works**\n1. **Input:** Paste contract text via **Form**.\n   - *Test Mode uses a sample \"NDA with unlimited liability\".*\n2. **Analyze:** **Gemini** scans for keywords like \"Liability\", \"Termination\", \"Jurisdiction\" and flags risks.\n3. **Report:** Generates a structured review (Risk Level, Summary, Fixes) and saves to **Google Sheets**.\n4. **Notify:** Sends the summary to **Slack**.\n\n**Setup steps**\n1. **Credentials:** Connect Gemini, Sheets, Slack.\n2. **Config:** Open **\"Config\"** to set Sheet ID.\n3. **Test:** Set `TEST_MODE` to `true`.",
